## Google recaptcha v3

Recaptcha v3 can be enabled in**WP admin  Voxel  Settings  Registration ** **Recaptcha**

Recaptcha affects **Login / Register (VX)** widget including login, registration, password reset and any other actions that can be performed on this widget.

Required fields:

- Site key
- Secret key

You can register your site and get these keys in the [v3 admin console](https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin)
